2. EASY AND CONVENIENT TO USE GOLF DIARY
- Synced with over 40,000 golf courses worldwide
- A clear and high-definition yardage book
- Convenient input your score
- Check the current shot location and distance
- Supports iOS/Android apps
3. AUTOMATIC REGISTRATION OF CLOUD
- Round records entered into a smart watch or smartphone are automatically registered in the cloud after your golf.

- Allows to classify records by year, by services and by record status
